                <img src="https://i1.wp.com/www.curiouskeeda.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/02/vagator-beach-goa.jpg?resize=640%2C480&ssl=1"
                    width="100%" height="auto"><br><br>

                <p>
                    If beaches are what you are searching for in North Goa, then, at that point here is another which
                    will fulfill you. Chapora Beach is another fascination in Goa which is an absolute necessity visit
                    on your get-away. It’s exceptional among different shorelines of Goa that contacts a concordance in
