                </p>

                <h3 style="text-align: center;">9|<br>
                    Dona Paula Beach</h3>

                <img src="https://i0.wp.com/www.curiouskeeda.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/02/Dona-paula.jpg?resize=640%2C425&ssl=1"
                    width="100%" height="auto"><br><br>

                <p>
                    Another best beaches in North Goa which is a must-visit for you is the Dona Paul Beach. Dona Paula
                    shoreline was named after the Portuguese Viceroy’s daughter Dona Paula de Menezes. This energetic,
                    young lady turned out to be miserably fascinated with a Goan fisherman. Clearly, this match was
                    unacceptable to the Viceroy who denied his daughter Dona Paula to meet her young darling again.
                </p>

                <p>
                    It was said that his little girl committed suicide and in her memory, the Viceroy named the beach
